HEADWORD: Multiplicand
<hw>Mul"ti*pli*cand`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>multiplicandus</ets> to be multiplied: cf. F.
<ets>multiplicande</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Math.)</fld> <def>The number
which is to be multiplied by another number called the
<corr>multiplier</corr>. See Note under
